result.name: Pici Pasta Bar (Shatin)

reviews.text: We stumbled across Pici and ended up ordering from the Brunch menu. Ludicrously good value; less than $400 for two top quality three course meals plus drinks is an absolute steal. Staff were lovely and the ambience is decent. More importantly the food is wholesome and delicious.

Delicious and very fresh Pasta!! Thank you to the staff to make our experience so wonderful. All the foods was so tasty!! Lots of space and many seats. Set dinner so can share. Also have a la carts. See you again Pici 😀

One of the bigger Pici restaurants and definitely the most easily accessible. Same pasta as any other place in this franchise - great pasta but lots of grease to go with it. Great decor on the big dining hall, but the staff sometimes has issues keeping up with all the guests at this particular restaurant.

The service in Shatin Pici is very good!! They’re so nice and passionate to recommend food for you, and the freshly made pasta is delicious for sure.   We had a set for two, just around $500 which is relatively cheap with this quality.

A very nice Italian restaurant that is famous for home made pasta. The quality is great, service is excellent. The price is slightly above average. Expatriate waiters /waitresses are available to serve so English is not a problem.

result.adr_address: 18 Sha Tin Centre St, Sha Tin, Hong Kong
result.formatted_address: 18 Sha Tin Centre St, Sha Tin, Hong Kong
result.name: New Town Plaza Phase 1

reviews.text:
The best shopping mall in Hong Kong:
1. itself + 6 more shopping malls, all inter-connected by enclosed air-conditioned walkways
2. Accessible by train, bus, minibuses, bicycles, private car (tons of parking space)
3. friendly affordable prices - not the Landmark or Pacific Place
It's easy to go around the place, convenient, but sometimes feel like the mall is kind of small.

It's the biggest mall in the region. Its been undergoing gentrification over the past few years. Local unique shops are being replaced by luxury chains. Car park is big but fills up quickly, and is expensive.
New Town Plaza Phase I is where you find the important shopping, City Super and lower level restaurant hall. There is direct access from the MTR Station and Shatin Park.
At Parkview : delicious food and good service👍

result.name: 沙田新城市廣場第一期

reviews.text: 商店按分類排列👍🏻
非常多內地客😥

成個商場嘅格局越嚟越似海港城，已經為自由行，而唔係再為沙田居民而設。
除非你真係好想買名牌，或者上食層食嘢，否則都係唔嚟好過！
小心俾自由行嘅巨型拖喼轆到隻腳， 成個商場比較行得舒服嘅係citysuper，起碼自由行唔會喺度買食材然後返屋企煮飯！
